desc: Zebra Skimmers prides itself in quality, but sometimes in shipping parts get scratched or dented and can no longer be sold to our traditional distribution partners. You are in luck with specially discounted, limited quantity items with the same great Zebra warranties.

layout.text:
Great pricing on tramp oil skimming products and acessories. Skimmers extend the lifetime of expensive metalworking coolant and reduce the costs of fluid disposal.

All products are new and feature our 90-day warranty.

Products are limited and will change often. All sales are final.
